table.name: reported_value_reporter_to_agent_metadata
table.viewSql: SELECT x.id, x.property_name, x.record_id, x.reporter_index, x."timestamp", x.data_type, x.bytes_value, x.boolean_value, x.number_value, x.string_value, x.enum_value, x.parent_name, x.latitude_value, x.longitude_value, x.public_key, x.authorized, x.metadata, x.reported_value_end_commit_num, x.reporter_end_commit_num, x.service_id FROM ( SELECT row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY join_tables.id ORDER BY join_tables.reporter_end_commit_num) AS rownum, join_tables.id, join_tables.property_name, join_tables.record_id, join_tables.reporter_index, join_tables."timestamp", join_tables.data_type, join_tables.bytes_value, join_tables.boolean_value, join_tables.number_value, join_tables.string_value, join_tables.enum_value, join_tables.parent_name, join_tables.latitude_value, join_tables.longitude_value, join_tables.reported_value_end_commit_num, join_tables.reporter_end_commit_num, join_tables.public_key, join_tables.authorized, join_tables.metadata, join_tables.service_id FROM ( SELECT reported_value.id, reported_value.property_name, reported_value.record_id, reported_value.reporter_index, reported_value."timestamp", reported_value.data_type, reported_value.bytes_value, reported_value.boolean_value, reported_value.number_value, reported_value.string_value, reported_value.enum_value, reported_value.parent_name, reported_value.latitude_value, reported_value.longitude_value, reported_value.end_commit_num AS reported_value_end_commit_num, reporter_to_agent_metadata.reporter_end_commit_num, reporter_to_agent_metadata.public_key, reporter_to_agent_metadata.authorized, reporter_to_agent_metadata.metadata, reported_value.service_id FROM (reported_value LEFT JOIN reporter_to_agent_metadata ON (((reported_value.record_id = reporter_to_agent_metadata.record_id) AND (reported_value.property_name = reporter_to_agent_metadata.property_name) AND (reported_value.reporter_index = reporter_to_agent_metadata.reporter_index) AND (reported_value.end_commit_num <= reporter_to_agent_metadata.reporter_end_commit_num))))) join_tables) x WHERE (x.rownum = 1);

table.name: reporter_to_agent_metadata
table.viewSql: SELECT x.id, x.property_name, x.record_id, x.public_key, x.authorized, x.reporter_index, x.metadata, x.service_id, x.reporter_end_commit_num FROM ( SELECT row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY join_tables.id ORDER BY join_tables.agent_end_commit_num) AS rownum, join_tables.id, join_tables.property_name, join_tables.record_id, join_tables.reporter_index, join_tables.authorized, join_tables.public_key, join_tables.reporter_end_commit_num, join_tables.agent_end_commit_num, join_tables.metadata, join_tables.service_id FROM ( SELECT reporter.id, reporter.property_name, reporter.record_id, reporter.reporter_index, reporter.authorized, reporter.public_key, reporter.end_commit_num AS reporter_end_commit_num, agent.end_commit_num AS agent_end_commit_num, agent.metadata, agent.service_id FROM (reporter LEFT JOIN agent ON (((reporter.public_key = (agent.public_key)::text) AND (reporter.end_commit_num <= agent.end_commit_num))))) join_tables) x WHERE (x.rownum = 1);
